Title: Frobenius-Schur Indicators, the Klein-bottle Amplitude, and the

Principle of Orbifold CovarianceAuthors: P. Bantay, (Rolland Eotvos University, Budapest)

Comments: 5 pages

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B488 (2000) 207-210

The "orbifold covariance principle", or OCP for short, is presented tosupport a conjecture of Pradisi, Sagnotti and Stanev on the expression of theKlein- bottle amplitude.